channel.description:
my run from my source was working fine the whole week,today i try to run again and i get this, [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/fsapi.jpg[/img]
can someone tell me how to fix it or can we use tv so u can fix it? i will rep++

item.title: I have problems to run my server...help please!
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

[quote=“blindlypowa, post:4, topic:428429”][quote author=Team_Rocket link=topic=531123.msg3879724#msg3879724 date=1325954586]
@Echo Off
Java -Xmx512m -cp .; Server

You’re welcome.
[/quote]

thanks man,this helped alot…its fixed now :)[/quote]

Yeah, you’re welcome. Lol and people say I don’t help.
